        "TileImage": "$($repository 38253678-92ae-438b-ab73-300cc5373553).Image",
        "Description": "Now that we were able to get into the phone, we tracked the call to the phone of one Diana Burnwood. Appearently she&apos;s a top handler of a spy conglomerate known as the &quot;ICA&quot;. Never heard of them a day in my life, but they are a subsidary of some secret society called &quot;The Ark Society&quot;. We&apos;re so many levels deep in this that Spymaster Pliskin himself is running overwatch on this op. kill Nathaniel, the Washington twins, Hagen, and the Constant, and enigmatic man with no traceable history.",
